flowchart LR
  U[Clinician / User] --> SH[Shell MFE\nReact 19 + Vite + Module Federation]
  SH --> VM[Voice MFE\nStart Session + Live Transcript]
  VM --> VAPI[Voice Service\n.NET 9]
  VAPI --> EVT1[Dapr Event\nTranscriptProduced]

  EVT1 --> AG[AI Agent Service\nSemantic Kernel Orchestration]
  AG --> DEC{Confidence + Triage Level}

  DEC -->|High confidence| TCOMP[TriageCompleted Event]
  DEC -->|Low confidence or High risk| ESC[EscalationRequired Event]

  ESC --> TM[Triage MFE\nHuman-in-the-loop Review]
  TM --> APPR[Clinician Approve / Override]
  APPR --> TCOMP

  TCOMP --> FHIR[FHIR Service]
  TCOMP --> NOTIF[Notification Service]
  TCOMP --> SCH[Scheduling Service]

  AG --> RT[Real-time Updates\nWeb PubSub / SignalR]
  RT --> SH

